headline: Real Estate Stocks Rise: Realty Income (O) & Simon Property (SPG) Lead Last Week’s Winners
summary: Markets have started the week on rocky footing. The Dow Jones is off 1.3% as of 1:45 p.m. ET in Monday trading, but real estate stocks are holding in relatively well.
